      "description": "Allows user to add a radar item:\nAttributes (one option only - mandatory):\nType: Threat or Oppotunity\nCategory: Business, Operating Model, Capabilities, People & Knowledge\nDistance: Detected, Assessing, Assessed or Responding, Responded\nImpact: Low, Medium or High\nTolerance: High, Medium or Low\nLink (one only, not mandatory)\nZoom In: a link to another radar - if the user clicks, will open the link\n\nUpdate and Delete will be supported\n",
